    <briefdescription>
<para>Component that formats arithmetic values into a display string. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds a std::vformat-compatible format string that accepts a single arithmetic argument. Used by binding systems to convert numeric game state (e.g. scores, health) into text for UiTextComponent.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>Score2UiTextUpdateSystem </para>
